  "text": "Then in general, I could say that if an individual has a close encounter with a UFO or any other type of experience that seems to be UFO related, he must look to the heart of the encounter and the effect upon him to determine whether it was Orion or Confederation contact. Is this correct? This is correct if there is fear and doom. The contact was quite likely of a negative nature if the result is hope, friendly feelings, and the awakening of a positive feeling of purposeful service to others. The marks of confederation, contact are evident.",
